mysql_groundtruth: SELECT DISTINCT SALES.BUYER_ID AS BUYER_ID FROM PRODUCT INNER JOIN SALES ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID WHERE PRODUCT_NAME = 'S8' AND SALES.BUYER_ID NOT IN ( SELECT SALES.BUYER_ID FROM PRODUCT INNER JOIN SALES ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID WHERE PRODUCT_NAME = 'iPhone')

SELECT s.buyer_id FROM Sales AS s INNER JOIN Product AS p ON s.product_id = p.product_id WHERE s.buyer_id IS NOT NULL GROUP BY s.buyer_id HAVING SUM(CASE WHEN p.product_name = 'S8' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) > 0 AND SUM(CASE WHEN p.product_name = 'iPhone' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = 0
